<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1235,225,324]" box="[199,1235,261,288]" pageId="7" pageNumber="138">Head. Clypeus bidentate with a notch to the side of each denticle. Antennae nine segmented.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1235,225,324]" box="[199,1143,297,324]" pageId="7" pageNumber="138">Pronotum. Very convex with lateral margins explanate, sometimes carinate laterally.</paragraph>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3993631" ID-Zenodo-Dep="3993631" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3993631/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="138" startId="7.[151,250,1954,1979]" targetBox="[169,1430,368,1806]" targetPageId="7">
<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1436,1954,2015]" pageId="7" pageNumber="138">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,274,1954,1979]" pageId="7" pageNumber="138">FIGURE 3.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authority="Scholtz &amp; Howden, 1987" authorityName="Scholtz &amp; Howden" authorityYear="1987" box="[279,793,1954,1979]" class="Insecta" family="Scarabaeidae" genus="Endroedyolus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="138" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="paradoxus">
<emphasis box="[279,531,1954,1978]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="138">Endroedyolus paradoxus</emphasis>
Scholtz &amp; 
<bibRefCitation author="Howden, H. F. &amp; Scholtz, C. H." box="[643,793,1954,1979]" pageId="7" pageNumber="138" pagination="155 - 192" refId="ref6380" refString="Howden, H. F. &amp; Scholtz, C. H. (1987) A revision of the African genus Odontoloma Boheman (Coleoptera: Scarabaeidae: Scarabaeinae). Journal of the Entomological Society of Southern Africa, 50, 155 - 192." type="journal article" year="1987">Howden, 1987</bibRefCitation>
